112
00:04:58,760 --> 00:05:00,359
what is it that we're contemplating?

113
00:05:00,359 --> 00:05:02,660
What is the object of our contemplation?

114
00:05:02,660 --> 00:05:04,579
Well, it's our lives.

115
00:05:04,579 --> 00:05:06,720
The Bible says in this portion of scripture

116
00:05:06,720 --> 00:05:08,359
in First Corinthians 11 and verse 28,

117
00:05:08,359 --> 00:05:09,440
notice the Bible says,

118
00:05:09,559 --> 00:05:13,600
but let a man examine, what's the next word?

119
