150
00:06:39,980 --> 00:06:41,579
Does my life please God?

151
00:06:41,579 --> 00:06:44,540
Do my actions please God?

152
00:06:45,519 --> 00:06:49,100
Do my thoughts please God?

153
00:06:49,100 --> 00:06:52,220
Do my words please God?

154
00:06:52,220 --> 00:06:54,339
I had this thought as I was just meditating

155
00:06:54,339 --> 00:06:56,739
upon this message for this evening

156
