189
00:08:45,940 --> 00:08:47,700
Right, and so we think about that.

190
00:08:47,700 --> 00:08:50,900
Sometimes we just, you ever hear somebody say,

191
00:08:50,900 --> 00:08:52,940
I'm gonna give him a piece of my mind?

192
00:08:52,940 --> 00:08:53,859
Be careful.

193
00:08:55,179 --> 00:08:58,099
You know how easy it is to sin with the tongue?

194
00:08:58,099 --> 00:09:01,979
Read the book of James, so easy.

195
00:09:01,979 --> 00:09:05,739
