00:11:16,059 --> 00:11:20,059
thankful to be redeemed, but we still have a sin nature

237
00:11:20,059 --> 00:11:24,059
and we understand this evening that when we go through that process of contemplation

238
00:11:24,059 --> 00:11:28,059
