00:11:56,059 --> 00:12:00,059
if we're not careful, we'll act like we don't need confession.

247
00:12:00,059 --> 00:12:04,059
That I really don't have anything. And then sometimes we'll say something like this,

248
00:12:04,059 --> 00:12:08,059
Lord, if I have sinned, would you forgive me? Hold on a minute, it's

