00:12:08,059 --> 00:12:12,059
not if I have sinned. Amen?

250
00:12:12,059 --> 00:12:16,059
We know that we have sinned. It's not this broad thing.

251
00:12:16,059 --> 00:12:20,059
Confession means to say the same thing about. It means to agree with God.

252
00:12:20,059 --> 00:12:24,059
When David confessed, when if you look in Psalm 51

253
00:12:24,059 --> 00:12:28,059
and you read the confession of David, you find

254
00:12:28,059 --> 00:12:32,059
that he is confessing. He is saying, this is wicked

255
00:12:32,059 --> 00:12:36,059
what I've done. He says, against thee and thee only have I

